casebody.data:
Leif HALVORSEN, petitioner,
v.
DeEdra HART, Warden. No. 18-8434. Supreme Court of the United States June 17, 2019. Motion of petitioner to defer consideration of petition for writ of certiorari denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
